    "We prompt GPT-4 to generate tasks for Privacy Policy QA, SQuADShifts Reddit, and Contract NLI.",
    "For simplicity, we use the same prompts from Appendix B.1 to generate questions and hypotheses (see Table 7).",
    "For Privacy Policy QA, we add a simple instruction prefix to answer the question with yes or no along with the question and the context to generate the answer.",
    "For extractive question answering, we add the prefix \"Extract the exact words from the paragraph for the question.",
    "If the question is not answerable, say N/A.\""
